      "comment": "CARISSA'S BABY (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 30.08 beating Dip The Donut. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from six starts. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. BROOKDENE (6) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 515m (29.86). Can do much better this time. LIZZY'S GIRL (1) improved her time on first attempt here at the trip with a 5.5 lengths third in 30.02 latest. Strong latest and expected to measure up. WYNBURN STYLE (4) is hard to fault of late and is a strong top-three hope again.",
